Microcontroller:-

Microcontroller" ke baare mein bataya hai. Microcontroller ek small computer chip hota hai jo ek electronic circuit board par mounted hota hai.
Microcontroller mein processor, memory, input/output ports, aur other peripherals shamil hote hain jo uske through 
electronic devices aur systems ko control karne mein use kiye jaate hain.

Is project mein microcontroller ka use karke hum sensors ko control karenge aur unki readings ko collect karenge. Microcontroller sensors 
se readings collect karke us data ko digital signals ke roop mein convert karta hai aur phir use cloud server ya other processing devices 
tak transmit karta hai.

Aap different microcontroller ka use kar sakte hain jaise Arduino, Raspberry Pi, ESP32, etc. In microcontrollers mein aapko sensors ke readings
ke sath-sath communication protocols jaise Wi-Fi, Bluetooth, LoRaWAN, etc. ke suppor
t bhi milte hain jiske through aap real-time data transfer kar sakte hain.
